msgstr "通常、入力されたメールアドレスが既存のアカウントと一致するとログインモーダルが自動的に開きます。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:84
msgid "Automatically generate a username and password."
msgstr "ユーザー名とパスワードを自動生成します。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:85
msgid "A password field is provided for the customer."
msgstr "顧客用のパスワードフィールドが提供されます。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:96
msgid "Automatically matches guest orders to user accounts."
msgstr "ゲスト注文をユーザーアカウントに自動的にマッチさせます。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:119
msgid "Enable or disable WooCommerce Order Notes field."
msgstr "WooCommerceの注文メモフィールドを有効または無効にします。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:135
msgid "Recommended to increase conversions."
msgstr "コンバージョンを増やすために推奨されます。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:148
msgid "Values are combined into a single address_1 field based on country."
msgstr "値は国に基づいて単一のaddress_1フィールドに結合されます。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:156
msgid "Choose how to display separate address 1 fields."
msgstr "別々のaddress 1フィールドの表示方法を選択します。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:166
msgid "Separate Address Fields is incompatible with Google Address Autocomplete."
msgstr "Separate Address FieldsはGoogle Address Autocompleteと互換性がありません。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:171
msgid "Replace first and last name fields with a single full name field."
msgstr "名前と姓のフィールドを単一のフルネームフィールドに置き換えます。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:178
msgid "Promote selected countries to the top of the countries list."
msgstr "選択した国を国リストの上部に昇格させます。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:196
msgid "Validate phone number entry based on selected country."
msgstr "選択した国に基づいて電話番号の入力を検証します。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:235
msgid "Choose which billing address fields are visible."
msgstr "表示する請求先住所フィールドを選択します。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:257
msgid "Enable or disable Google Address Autocomplete feature."
msgstr "Google Address Autocomplete機能を有効または無効にします。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:264
msgid "Enable or disable Fetchify address autocomplete feature."
msgstr "Fetchify住所自動補完機能を有効または無効にします。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:280
msgid "Validates shipping address with Smarty.com."
msgstr "Smarty.comで配送先住所を検証します。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:289
msgid "Smarty Auth ID."
msgstr "Smarty認証ID。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:296
msgid "Smarty Auth Token."
msgstr "Smarty認証トークン。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:310
msgid "Allows customer to remove or adjust quantity of cart items at checkout."
msgstr "顧客がチェックアウト時にカート内商品の数量を削除または調整できるようにします。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:319
msgid "Displays an edit link under cart items."
msgstr "カート内商品の下に編集リンクを表示します。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:326
msgid "When hovering over an item, show a button (X) to remove it."
msgstr "アイテムにカーソルを合わせると、削除ボタン（X）を表示します。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:333
msgid "URL to redirect to when customer empties cart from checkout page."
msgstr "顧客がチェックアウトページからカートを空にしたときにリダイレクトするURL。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:343
msgid "Cart summary sticks to the top when scrolling."
msgstr "スクロール時にカート概要が上部に固定されます。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:364
msgid "Show coupon field above payment gateways on mobile devices."
msgstr "モバイルデバイスで支払いゲートウェイの上にクーポンフィールドを表示します。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:368
msgid "Enable Mobile Cart Summary is not compatible with Enable Mobile Coupon Field."
msgstr "モバイルカート概要の有効化はモバイルクーポンフィールドの有効化と互換性がありません。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:373
msgid "Show the credit card logos on mobile."
msgstr "モバイルでクレジットカードのロゴを表示します。"

#: client/ts/admin/Components/CheckoutEditor/panels/CheckoutSettingsPanel.tsx:379
msgid "Example: Show order summary and coupons."
msgstr "例：注文概要とクーポンを表示します。"

